transformers_text: 593 15 Save Nami Luffy's Fight on the Snow Capped Mountains Transliteration Nami o Suk ue Ru fi Yu kiyama no Tata kai Japanese Yoshihiro Ueda J in Tanaka April 28 2013 2013 04 28 October 23 2022 Chopper tells the others that Nami was kidnapped by the Yeti Cool Brothers Luffy and Franky go after them but Franky in Chopper's body goes against Chopper's warnings and takes a rumble ball going on a rampage and chasing Luffy Meanwhile Caesar notices Vega punk's beam in Franky's body and craves for it he calls his men so they go to the fire side gate and see a cave After Luffy nearly falls into a trap he faces the Yeti Cool Brothers when Franky ending up beating one of them before his rampaging forces Luffy to knock him out The second brother tries to escape with Nami before Law appears and defeats him Law then proposes an alliance to take down an Emperor to survive in the New World
